               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400615-name-752" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400615-name-752" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400615-name-752" type="surname" value="PIGGOTT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400615-name-752" type="given" value="DAVID"></interp>DAVID PIGGOTT.</persName>
                  </hi>I am Captain of the barge <hi rend="italic">Mary Sarah</hi>. The prisoner was employed by me to work on board. On the 1st of June I missed a pair of boots from the cabin, which I had seen safe on the Saturday night before—these are them—(<hi rend="italic">looking at them</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. He lent them to me to wear. <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi>. I never did.</p>
